{"tid":197282,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"黃貓尋領養","createTime":"2017-04-11T19:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T13:46:25.000Z","uid":72269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8bbd0a74e3f61b258d4373a87e0b8139460ce2","tid":197282,"uid":72269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"話說之前係個貓義工度領養左隻貓。本身佢有3隻等人領養，而我就揀左隻3色貓，另一隻亦都好快有人領養左。由我領養貓貓到依家已經過左三個月，最後一隻至今仲未有適合嘅領養人，所以我係度代呢位貓義工出post，希望可以幫佢快啲搵到屋企。<br />\n貓貓叫蛋卷，一歲(仲係好活躍架)，打左第一針，未絕育<br />\n鍾意俾人抱同煲水<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s47urvi9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs47urvi9&h=e353ab60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vhg0prye\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvhg0prye&h=cf3698bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位貓義工好好，知道我係學生住公屋都俾我領養，冇過問我嘅家庭,經濟能力。亦都會俾你探貓先決定領養與否。<br />\n<br />\n如有意領養，可以tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Barbiebu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBarbiebu&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4f2af9fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Barbiebu</a><br />\n我會留底義工嘅聯絡方法"},{"pid":"647fc06866fda7676cf78de83ba19246ddf0f463","tid":197282,"uid":72269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:50:12.000Z","msg":"附上我家主子j圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/epw2kfrt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fepw2kfrt&h=40553734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢位貓義工度領養嘅3色貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/961hjmrs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F961hjmrs&h=995c597d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係另一位貓義工度領養<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ynp18at0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fynp18at0&h=a33e4311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cd9c8c790b1317eff4580b25ad04e4171451313","tid":197282,"uid":5